{"article_id":"EBuBRqsKPevL07h7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump said this weekend","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"that he will try to speed an appeal","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"after a federal judge late Friday halted his plans","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"to construct border wall","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"by declaring a national emergency","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"and pulling the money from the Pentagon .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Mr. Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"writing on Twitter from Japan ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"where he was traveling ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"lashed out at Judge Haywood Gilliam , an Obama appointee to the federal court for Northern California ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"he was enabling criminals","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"by ruling against the president ' s most prominent campaign promise .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Judge Gilliam said","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"the president and his team overstepped their powers","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"by trying to rearrange money within the Pentagon","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"to make it usable for border wall construction ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"after Congress had a thorough debate","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"and approved far less","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"than the president wanted .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"He issued a preliminary injunction","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"finding","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"that Congress is likely to prevail","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"as the case proceeds ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"and he blocked the government from carrying out wall-building","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"was already underway near El Paso , Texas , and Yuma , Arizona .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"\" Congress has repeatedly rejected legislation","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that would have funded substantially broader border barrier construction , \"","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"the judge wrote .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"The ruling is a substantial blow to Mr. Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"who orchestrated a government shutdown","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"to try to get his border wall built ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"then signed a bill","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"to reopen government","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"without getting the wall money","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"he sought .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"He had been counting on his emergency powers ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"he said","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"allowed him to tap the Pentagon ' s money","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"to build border barriers .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Indeed , one section of law explicitly authorized the Defense Department to build barriers in drug corridors .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"But the pot of money for that construction was limited ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"and the Defense Department had to siphon money from other accounts","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"to fill the drug corridor fund","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"- something","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Judge Gilliam said","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"isn ' t allowed in this case .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"The Justice Department had argued","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"that Congress didn ' t explicitly deny the administration the ability","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"to use the money ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"and in fact included reprogramming abilities in the laws","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"allowing the administration to shift substantial amounts of money within the Defense Department .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Indeed , that ' s exactly what House Democrats have done in their new round of spending bills for next year ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"moving to explicitly prevent the president from a repeat of this year ' s emergency declaration money-shifting .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"But Judge Gilliam said","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that ' s not necessary .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"the Constitution doesn ' t require Congress to foresee every circumstance","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"in which the president might make mischief with money .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"Instead , the president is bound only to spend on exactly what Congress authorizes .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"\" Defendants ' reading of these provisions ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"if accepted ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"would pose serious problems under the Constitution ' s separation of powers principles , \"","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"he concluded .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Mr. Trump didn ' t comment on Judge Gilliam ' s legal reasoning ,","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"but on Twitter said","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"he was hurting the country ' s safety .","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"\" Another activist","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Obama appointed judge","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"has just ruled against us on a section of the Southern Wall","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"that is already under construction .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"This is a ruling against Border Security and in favor of crime , drugs and human trafficking .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"We are asking for an expedited appeal ! \"","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"Mr. Trump initially requests about $ 1.6 billion in border wall money for 2019 ,","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"then upped that request to $ 5 billion , and eventually $ 5.7 billion .","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"Congress , after an election , one government shutdown and a change in power in the House , approved $ 1.375 billion .","depth":4},{"id":78,"text":"Mr. Trump signed that legislation in February","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"- then immediately declared a national emergency","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and issued a memo","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"authorizing the Defense Department to tap $ 2.5 billion in drug interdiction accounts and another $ 3.6 billion in military construction funds","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"to build the wall .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"He also authorized use of $ 601 million from a Treasury Department forfeiture fund .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"Under the law , the drug interdiction money can be used","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"to build walls in drug corridors ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"but the fund didn ' t have $ 2.5 billion ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"so the Defense Department said","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"it would reprogram money from elsewhere","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"to fill out those accounts .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"It authorized $ 1 billion in transfers .","depth":7},{"id":91,"text":"That ' s the money","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"Judge Gilliam halted .","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"He did not rule on the government ' s plans","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"to tap the $ 3.6 billion in emergency declaration money ,","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"that issue is not yet ripe .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"given the tenor and reasoning in Friday ' s opinion ,","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"it ' s difficult to imagine Judge Gilliam would find use of that money for a border wall legal at this point .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"Judge Gilliam is one of several courts","depth":2},{"id":101,"text":"hearing challenges to Mr. Trump ' s emergency declaration .","depth":3},{"id":102,"text":"Cases in Texas and Washington , D.C. , are still proceeding .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":205,"left":202,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":177,"right":201,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":168,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":132,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":115,"right":1